# Privacy Policy

**Yahoo Finance History to CSV** (this extension) does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data to external servers.

- **Storage**: The extension uses Chrome’s local storage only to save your language preference (EN/KO). This data stays on your device.
- **Yahoo Finance**: The extension runs only on `finance.yahoo.com` history pages. It reads the visible table on the page you have open and builds a CSV in your browser. No page data is sent to us or any third party.
- **No analytics, no accounts, no tracking.**

Last updated: 2026.
